      "score": 0.044500699575633226,
      "text": "Charles Smith Olden\nCharles Smith Olden (February 19, 1799April 7, 1876) was an American Republican Party politician, who served as the 19th Governor of New Jersey from 1860 to 1863 during the first part of the American Civil War.",
